        "html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 40px 80px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:5fr 4fr;gap:0;min-height:540px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 32px rgba(60,30,10,0.08);\">\n    <div style=\"background:#F0E7DA;padding:56px 48px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;\">\n      <div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#D4874B;margin:0 0 24px;\">1인 사업가를 위한 강의</p>\n        <h1 style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,3.6vw,46px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.22;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#241C14;margin:0 0 24px;\">Claude가 있어도<br>막히는 이유,<br><span style=\"color:#5C3D1E;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:#D4874B;text-underline-offset:6px;\">코어 캠퍼스가 풉니다.</span></h1>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:#6B5040;margin:0 0 32px;max-width:380px;\">도구는 있는데 방법을 모르는 1인 사업가를 위해 실무 구조부터 설계합니다. 단계별 시리즈 강의로, 한 번에 하나씩.</p>\n        <a href=\"/courses\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#5C3D1E;color:#F7F3ED;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;padding:15px 36px;border-radius:8px;\">내 강의 찾기</a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;background:#E8D8C4;color:#5C3D1E;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500;\"># Claude 활용</span>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;background:#E8D8C4;color:#5C3D1E;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500;\"># 1인 사업 자동화</span>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;background:#E8D8C4;color:#5C3D1E;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500;\"># 콘텐츠 설계</span>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;background:#E8D8C4;color:#5C3D1E;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500;\"># 수익화 구조</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:#3A2210;padding:48px 40px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-start;gap:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C99A6B;margin:0 0 8px;\">강의 구성</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#4A2E18;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#C99A6B;min-width:36px;\">01</span>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#F0E7DA;margin:0 0 4px;\">Claude 실무 기초 세팅</p>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#9A7A60;margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">업무에 붙이는 첫 번째 구조 만들기</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"background:#4A2E18;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#C99A6B;min-width:36px;\">02</span>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#F0E7DA;margin:0 0 4px;\">콘텐츠 생산 파이프라인</p>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#9A7A60;margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">반복 작업을 시스템으로 전환</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"background:#4A2E18;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#C99A6B;min-width:36px;\">03</span>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#F0E7DA;margin:0 0 4px;\">수익화 구조 설계</p>\n            <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#9A7A60;margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">강의·서비스·자동화를 연결하는 방법</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid #5A3820;\">\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#7A5A40;margin:0 0 12px;\">다음 기수 모집 중</p>\n        <a href=\"/enroll\" style=\"display:block;background:#C99A6B;color:#1A0A02;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;padding:13px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">사전 등록하기</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
